<div class="main">
	<div class="container">	
		<h1 style="text-align: center">Dear {{firstName}} {{lastName}}!</h1>
		<p>Based on your watch history, we would like to recommend you the following deals:</p>
		<table class="games">
			<thead>
				<tr>
					<th>Name</th>
					<th>Store</th>
					<th>Discounted price</th>
				</tr>
			</thead>
			<tbody>
				{{#each recommendedGames}}
				<tr>
					<td>{{this.name}}</td>
					<td><a href="{{this.stores.linkToGame}}">{{this.stores.name}}</a></td>
					<td>{{this.stores.specialPrice}}â‚¬</td>
				</tr>
				{{/each}}
			</tbody>
		</table>
		<p>You received this message, because you subscribed to our newsletters. If you dont want to receive newsletters in the future, you can unsubscribe at anytime by going to <a href="{{siteUrl}}/profile/details">profile/details</a> or by clicking on the following button:</p>
		<div class="button-container">
			<a href="{{unsubscribeURL}}">Unsubscribe</a>
		</div>
		<p>
			If the button doesn't work, please copy and paste the following link into your browser's address bar and press enter:
			<br>
			<a href="{{unsubscribeURL}}">{{unsubscribeURL}}</a>
		</p>
		<p><b>Sincerely,<br>{{ siteName }}</b></p>
	</div>
</div>